Posted By: David Seaborn
All,

I have decided to sell much of my 19th Century baseball collcetion.  I have listed the cards with their grades and prices below.  Scans of most of the cards can be seen by clicking the link below (note:  Only the cards listed here are for sale, some on the photobucket site are not for sale).  If you'd like an additional scan, just send an email (oldorioles@aol.com).  Please email me with interest and I will get back to you in the order I receive the emails.  I'll try to keep this page current as the cards sell.  Thanks much, Dave
